data.description: Welcome home! This cozy, 3 bedroom and 3 full bath home in Rising Sun sits on a .47 acre wooded lot.   Extended off the primary bedroom is a heated sitting room that has access to the back deck and overlooks the private, wooded property. The two-car garage allows for space for your vehicles and extra storage.  The owners have invested in maintaining the property and updating the bathrooms and other living spaces, perfect for relaxing after work or hosting get-togethers with family and friends.  The finished basement and laundry room adds additional space for storage and living.  This home is ready for you to move in and enjoy!
